  "detailed_description": "<h1>Add to your wish list!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1746550521\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Airfleet - your own airline is in your hands! Manage every aspect of the business: from thoughtful route planning to precise crew selection, every decision affects the reputation and efficiency of the company.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/ff39d3b281e722667d7cf3b58de6a22f.avif?t=1746550521\" width=652 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/54ae7cf9ffbc83024d68f32419d207fe.poster.avif?t=1746550521\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/54ae7cf9ffbc83024d68f32419d207fe.webm?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/54ae7cf9ffbc83024d68f32419d207fe.mp4?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Create an extensive transportation network, combining major international terminals with cozy provincial airfields. Optimize connections and logistics, turning each airport into a vital hub for your empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/edad256df8b3f47d6091d1a6a546c71a.avif?t=1746550521\" width=652 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/d53e47cca5cbcf636f180d4fb742811e.poster.avif?t=1746550521\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/d53e47cca5cbcf636f180d4fb742811e.webm?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/d53e47cca5cbcf636f180d4fb742811e.mp4?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Choose your strategy: become a leader in mass budget transportation or create an elite service for demanding customers. A variety of classes allows you to customize comfort and pricing, gaining passenger trust and loyalty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/1ac04999c4a7c8b806b8de11ed6494d4.avif?t=1746550521\" width=652 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/34c057a347579a8ab5524f90192341a6.poster.avif?t=1746550521\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/34c057a347579a8ab5524f90192341a6.webm?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/34c057a347579a8ab5524f90192341a6.mp4?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Build a unique fleet of more than 11 detailed recreations of civilian vehicles from around the world. Transport passengers on modern airliners, regional jets and fuel-efficient turboprops to meet every demand.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/625925004914a82766746f96c742d514.avif?t=1746550521\" width=652 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/2715a8369646262266384e8201d7a176.poster.avif?t=1746550521\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/2715a8369646262266384e8201d7a176.webm?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/2715a8369646262266384e8201d7a176.mp4?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use the color theme customization to make the look of the game pleasing to you!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Airfleet - your own airline is in your hands! Manage every aspect of the business: from thoughtful route planning to precise crew selection, every decision affects the reputation and efficiency of the company.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/ff39d3b281e722667d7cf3b58de6a22f.avif?t=1746550521\" width=652 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/54ae7cf9ffbc83024d68f32419d207fe.poster.avif?t=1746550521\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/54ae7cf9ffbc83024d68f32419d207fe.webm?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/54ae7cf9ffbc83024d68f32419d207fe.mp4?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Create an extensive transportation network, combining major international terminals with cozy provincial airfields. Optimize connections and logistics, turning each airport into a vital hub for your empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/edad256df8b3f47d6091d1a6a546c71a.avif?t=1746550521\" width=652 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/d53e47cca5cbcf636f180d4fb742811e.poster.avif?t=1746550521\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/d53e47cca5cbcf636f180d4fb742811e.webm?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/d53e47cca5cbcf636f180d4fb742811e.mp4?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Choose your strategy: become a leader in mass budget transportation or create an elite service for demanding customers. A variety of classes allows you to customize comfort and pricing, gaining passenger trust and loyalty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/1ac04999c4a7c8b806b8de11ed6494d4.avif?t=1746550521\" width=652 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/34c057a347579a8ab5524f90192341a6.poster.avif?t=1746550521\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/34c057a347579a8ab5524f90192341a6.webm?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/34c057a347579a8ab5524f90192341a6.mp4?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Build a unique fleet of more than 11 detailed recreations of civilian vehicles from around the world. Transport passengers on modern airliners, regional jets and fuel-efficient turboprops to meet every demand.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/625925004914a82766746f96c742d514.avif?t=1746550521\" width=652 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/2715a8369646262266384e8201d7a176.poster.avif?t=1746550521\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/2715a8369646262266384e8201d7a176.webm?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1421380/extras/2715a8369646262266384e8201d7a176.mp4?t=1746550521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use the color theme customization to make the look of the game pleasing to you!</p>",
